episodes.title: It's Hard To Believe! She Created A Cult That Killed Her! | True Crime Documentary
episodes.description:
A terrible true crime story about a woman who founded her own cult, where she proclaimed herself the Mother of God. Later, her own cult destroyed her! This case shocked everyone! The Case Of Amy Carlson.
